data.description: MUST SEE this beautiful and spacious 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home on a large fenced corner lot with plenty of mature trees.  Kitchen has plenty of custom cabinets, granite countertops and a walk-in pantry next to the laundry room.  The 2-car garage was converted into a large bedroom with a half bath and a closet, but may be converted back to a garage, if desired. The garage door is still attached/installed.  This location is ideal, close to schools, fire department, IH-2, shopping centers, restaurants, a splash pad, and so much more!  Don't hesitate. Schedule your showing today.
